                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="15178403" author="devaraj" created="Thu, 3 Mar 2016 19:14:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The point to note is that responses from secondaries are always flagged as &quot;stale&quot;, even if the secondary does have the latest updates... Without addressing that, it&apos;s not easy to address this jira.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15178535" author="eclark" created="Thu, 3 Mar 2016 20:11:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;From the point of view of the client all responses from meta can be stale. So just assume that any secondary is good on the first time and after that go to the primary.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15178565" author="devaraj" created="Thu, 3 Mar 2016 20:26:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;True that.. Nice idea.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
